response.overview: Relive 25 years of The Undertaker's most dangerous matches and fiercest opponents. See How The Dead Man seal The Ugandan Giant Kamala in the WWE's first ever Casket Match. Feel the terror as The Undertaker and Mankind will battle to put each other six feet under in a Buried Alive Match. Witness the first ever Inferno Match in WWE history against Kane, and much more.
response.title: The Undertaker's Gravest Matches
